## updated_at 自動更新トリガー

```sql
CREATE OR REPLACE FUNCTION update_updated_at_column()
RETURNS TRIGGER AS $$
BEGIN
  NEW.updated_at = NOW();
  RETURN NEW;
END;
$$ LANGUAGE plpgsql;

-- 各テーブルにトリガー設定
CREATE TRIGGER update_reservations_updated_at
  BEFORE UPDATE ON reservations
  FOR EACH ROW
  EXECUTE FUNCTION update_updated_at_column();
```
